Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{part a}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come what may, I will have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed, and made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will move forward, taking pride in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As I always have, and I always will.
