Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a moody little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
