Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:07.38,KG1,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fsp2\fscx460\fscy373\pos(424,395)\c&HEBEBEB&\alpha&H80&}SHRINE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the place while I'm gone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the priests if something happens, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What else...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Count your tears, crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari won't be around to save you, wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Familiars aren't capable of ill-will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a member of the Shrine now. Keep your head held high,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.55,uniplanet,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\shad1\alpha&H50&\4a&HDD&\c&H644A56&\fscx77\fscy108\move(650,298,650,476,25,4238)}Planet{\c&H2F3234&}ary Union \N{\c&H422C6C&}Shrine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.47,0:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the child the Fox took in is one of us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what that Fox is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows if that child is a human or a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those red eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't skip your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get stronger and face them head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's what your mom would say, Koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do the best you can, shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll play with you when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though Sensei never spoke of her much,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a vague understanding that my mother was alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, to navigate a life filled with many unpleasant adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as a handful of sympathetic ones, I think that knowledge was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Koto, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we stop Koto-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Koto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your arms closer to your body when you punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with that student and her teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These acts are not worthy of one who would wear the fox mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,High Priest, I beg you to address this problem directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari! Koto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard him, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I think it's their fault for messing around during training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And for not apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And for being weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Might I suggest you take a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of your students while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! No! No! No! No! I don't want you to do that, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But this teacher is having doubts about his teaching methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to lend him a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In a wonderland they lie, dreaming as the days go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mumbling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, mumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You were thinking about the Mirror Capital again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good kick. You put your weight into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should praise you for training hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be number one at the Shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The crybaby I knew sure has grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As a teacher, I'm very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I might end up being stronger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you'll be the teacher, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go find Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet her and talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask her about Dad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Sensei, you already know the truth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Koto,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll make it there one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where summer dies and is born anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradise lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The place beyond the mirror, where the gravestones of memories stand in neat rows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Another ruckus again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see everyone's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two types of people in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who inconvenience me and those who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm having fun here in my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I really do want to see you and the others, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no clue when I'll be able to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but one day, let's all be together.
